article.description: — Bryan Antoine's 30 points led Radford past Elon 82-72 on Sunday.
article.headline: Antoine scores 30, Radford takes down Elon 82-72
article.linkText: Antoine scores 30, Radford takes down Elon 82-72
article.story: RADFORD, Va. -- — Bryan Antoine's 30 points led Radford past Elon 82-72 on Sunday. Antoine also had seven rebounds for the Highlanders (6-4). Justin Archer added 12 points while going 5 of 7 and 2 of 3 from the free throw line, and they also had 11 rebounds. Chandler Turner had 12 points and went 5 of 10 from the field. The Phoenix (5-4) were led in scoring by TK Simpkins, who finished with 23 points. Kendall Campbell added 15 points, seven rebounds and two blocks for Elon. In addition, Zac Ervin finished with 12 points. NEXT UP Radford plays Saturday against North Carolina Central at home, and Elon visits UNC Greensboro on Sunday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
